      "post_content": "Basically the arcbound lord. I'm sure it doesn't need to be said, but playing a Modular deck with him can get extremely out-of-hand for your opponents very quickly. I especially like the idea of teaming him up with Arcbound Reclaimer. Modular dude dies, feeds an Arcbound Crusher or something, Overseer makes everything bigger, Reclaimer resurrects the dead Modular dude, it dies again, feeds the Crusher, rinse, repeat. Fun.",
